// 1. Replaced "var" with "Holder storage" to explicitly define storage variable.
// 2. Removed "payable" from Collect function as it is not necessary.
// 3. Replaced "msg.sender.call.value(_am)()" with "msg.sender.transfer(_am)" to prevent reentrancy vulnerability.
// 4. Used "require" to add conditions for Collect function to execute.
